    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors are not assessed, consistent with MRL 2 requirements. Hemolysis index prediction error of 14.8% is within the 25% acceptance criterion. Package submitted under ProfileMinimal; no Context of Use object is included in this submission.",
